{"tid":1420177,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民間記者會唔係起大台,而家起緊公民大會","createTime":"2019-08-06T03:57:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T04:47:01.000Z","uid":14918,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d2c4e8ee17e36295b7073adadc8d030be5d0d107","tid":1420177,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:57:21.000Z","msg":"難怪港共同一毛咁撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n參考古希臘, 只要堅守原則, 就唔怕咩大台, 人人都係大台<br />\n<br />\n雅典集會或雅典公民大會（Ecclesia），建立於古希臘的黃金時代（公元前480年－前404年）。人們經常聚集到雅典城的廣場中，對城內的事務進行探討和投票。<span style=\"color: red;\">人群中沒有代表，所以任何人都可以提議議題來投票，</span>每個人都需要進行表決，結果採用多數決。為了使這個組織產生效果並具有公信力，至少6000人參與使得整個過程獲得其正當性。<br />\n<br />\n對雅典人來說，這種政府體制的優越性在於任何人都可以提供一項討論議題，每個人在投票過程中作出自己的選擇，這種方法促進了民主的發展。人民控制他們的政府使人們更高興，因為他們可以堅持自己的意見並發揮作用，而不是通過一個官方團體或專斷組織，甚至某個人來代替他們作出選擇。"},{"pid":"d66575adb1ca2a3ba8f2c8de2ff94d0ece9d4b3d","tid":1420177,"uid":39205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:59:50.000Z","msg":"幫連仔講返句公道說話<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1420183\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1420183</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1068940e70db30e7f37944eb38868d21a9e9ddb8","tid":1420177,"uid":108337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:13:02.000Z","msg":"公民記者會係做轉發<br />\nBtw， 絲打請代表我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"645d7ef34a34efed7e321d645af4cfc2ceb65ea8","tid":1420177,"uid":14918,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1068940e70db30e7f37944eb38868d21a9e9ddb8","tid":1420177,"uid":108337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:13:02.000Z","msg":"公民記者會係做轉發<br />\nBtw， 絲打請代表我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:14:33.000Z","msg":"唔係 &lsquo;請代表我&rsquo;, 而家&rsquo;認同&rsquo;<br />\n &lsquo;Aye&rsquo; or &lsquo;yes&rsquo;<br />\n&lsquo;nay&rsquo; or &lsquo;no&rsquo;"},{"pid":"5850165c9b7a84b7bcd686932af446adb75a45b1","tid":1420177,"uid":14918,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:18:46.000Z","msg":"唔好覺得林鄭昨日係行岩棋<br />\n我地既一舉一動都可以令林鄭呢一步棋失效<br />\n因為港共前設預左每日都有勇武手足出來, 然後開4PM狗會抹黑<br />\n但我地可以令呢一件事唔會發生<br />\n<br />\n另外港共除左搵狗之外, 都搵唔到人出來開記招而又唔會比人鬧<br />\n睇下林鄭就知, 基本上佢一出黎就神憎鬼厭 (EVEN 不同陣營)<br />\n所以佢先潛水<br />\n<br />\n而家就係和理非優會合<br />\n開文宣MAXIMUM 既時間啦!!!!"},{"pid":"6b2327e4cfdde07f931ea67bcab4d39d2ebe2564","tid":1420177,"uid":55010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:20:06.000Z","msg":"十分認同"},{"pid":"59c8944b1279c6587de1f4219dbb00b10bb27756","tid":1420177,"uid":14918,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:25:12.000Z","msg":"出面咁多人反, 睇得出對家真係好驚"},{"pid":"b3f278567fbff77701b1a6c15d56ebb51bad630d","tid":1420177,"uid":210612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:26:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8292e49edaf7a918c9fe51bf7661e7dac3d7aa8f","tid":1420177,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:27:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">參考古希臘, 只要堅守原則, 就唔怕咩大台, 人人都係大台</span>"},{"pid":"fbb84273cc9da605b03062d592940c2bcb1ba97f","tid":1420177,"uid":292798,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:28:20.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">絕對唔答任何問題，所有問題都係政府答</span></strong>"},{"pid":"d6460d653a068a8a9873cbcf3fd7200527da3b1d","tid":1420177,"uid":242083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:30:42.000Z","msg":"公民大會"},{"pid":"934dbf48f4a11ee46e77e67c42044b7c8d8ca444","tid":1420177,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:34:45.000Z","msg":"參考古希臘, 只要堅守原則, 就唔怕咩大台, 人人都係大台"},{"pid":"cbb8927bc41aabdc13615